data.description: This stunning all-brick, 3 bed/2 bath, 2274 sqft home has vast amounts of storage space! It is located on .76 acres with a wooden privacy fenced and truly is a dream come true! This home features an open entry way and high ceilings throughout the living space. There is also an abundance of natural light thanks to the many large windows. The primary bedroom is on the main level, bathroom walls and shower have an epoxy finish so no grout to clean! The FROG can double as a fourth bedroom or an office. The resort style back yard is magnificent. The covered patio is so large that it has two fans. The outdoor kitchen has a drop-in Napoleon natural gas grill. The gorgeous in-ground saltwater pool has a new pump as of 2023! Be sure to come and view this home.
